        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">The remaining amount of unreacted chloroacetic acid is assumed to leave the production process with the waste water. Further it was assumed that this wastewater is treated in a internal wastewater plant. The removal efficiency for chloroacetic acid is assumed with 90%. The carbon contained in the removed chloroacetic acid is accounted as CO2 emissions to air.</comment>
